Geogram (vendored subset for PolyMesh / Polyhedral-FEA)
=======================================================

This tree vendors BSD-3-Clause sources extracted from Bruno Lévy's Geogram
project (Inria / ALICE lineage). We do **not** vendor the full Geogram tree
(GUI, unused formats, Graphite, etc.).

